00:42:58.179 --> 00:43:08.179
There's a vision in Chapter 6 of Revelation, where the sixth seals open and the sky's darken and the army commanders hide in caves.

00:43:08.179 --> 00:43:19.179
That vision impressed me so much that I decided to serve Jehovah. That meant that I would have to leave the army because witnesses are neutral.

00:43:19.179 --> 00:43:26.179
