00:43:44.179 --> 00:43:52.179
I left and went to the hallway. I prayed to Jehovah. I want to serve you. What should I do? Help me find a way out of this.

00:43:52.179 --> 00:44:02.179
When I opened my eyes, another army officer approached and greeted me using my name. I still don't know who he is. He asked me, what do you need?

00:44:02.179 --> 00:44:11.179
I explained that I wanted to resign in order to become a Jehovah's Witness. He said, don't worry, give me your papers. I'm the colonel's assistant.

00:44:11.179 --> 00:44:20.179
Within 20 minutes, my discharge papers were ready and approved. In a short period of time, I became a publisher and I got baptized as one of Jehovah's Witnesses.

00:44:20.179 --> 00:44:26.179
At this time, I've been serving happily and Bethel for over 11 years with my wife, Hyell.

